text: Jean-Luc Préel (30 October 1940 - 3 September 2015) was a French politician. He was a member of the National Assembly from 1988 until 2012. He represented the Vendée department, and was a member of the New Centre. He was born in Caen. Préel died on 3 September 2015 in La Roche-sur-Yon, aged 74. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2015 deaths Category:Politicians from Normandy Category:People from Caen
